#why-us.ht-home-header.col-md-12
.col-md-12.why-us.rotate30.ptop70.pbottom100
  .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.text-center.mbottom40.rotate-30
    %span.header-text.white-fg WHY US
  .container.rotate-30
    .col-md-12.no-mar-pad
      .col-md-2
        %span.img-responsive.pad.pull-right.why-us-size.why-us-1-sprite
      .col-md-4
        %p.y-u.pad
          %strong
            12/7 Support
          %br
          When something goes wrong, just let us know and we’ll make it right. It’s as simple as that. Cocociti Experience Managers are just a call away; 9 am to 9 pm.
      .col-md-2
        %span.img-responsive.pad.pull-right.why-us-size.why-us-2-sprite
      .col-md-4
        %p.y-u.pad
          %strong
            Curated listings & Trusted Vendors
          %br
          Every vendor on Cocociti is handpicked for quality products & exceptional service; be it products or our delivery partners. Individual listings are made available by our expert curators.

    .col-md-12.no-mar-pad
      .col-md-2
        %span.img-responsive.pad.pull-right.why-us-size.why-us-3-sprite
      .col-md-4
        %p.y-u.pad
          %strong
            Safe payments & Fast Refunds
          %br
          All transactions are facilitated through our secure system with payment protection. Your money is kept in an escrow till the end of the renting tenure & security deposit is refunded once product is returned in good condition.
      .col-md-2
        %span.img-responsive.pad.pull-right.why-us-size.why-us-4-sprite
      .col-md-4
        %p.y-u.pad
          %strong
            Live Better
          %br
          Your email & number is not shared until a booking is confirmed. Say yes to peace of mind & no to annoying calls & spam mails.

#list-product.ht-home-header.col-md-12.hidden
.container.hidden
  .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.text-center.mbottom40
    %span.header-text MAKE MONEY, WISE
  .col-md-12.pbottom20
    %p.list-p-p
      Cocociti is a smart way to earn money by renting stuff. All you need to do is to click few pics, upload it to Cocociti, and mention your terms! You set the price for your listings, your availability, and booking requirements. You can message users and approve rentals as per your choice.
    %center
      %strong
        %h3.website-color
          LET YOUR THINGS WORK FOR YOU!
      %br
      %br
      = link_to new_product_path, class: "pa" do
        List Your Item

.tag-bg.col-md-12
  .container.hidden-xs
    .row.tag-mar
      - Category.root.each_slice(4) do |slice|
        .col-md-12.no-mar-pad
          - slice.each do |cat|
            .col-md-12.no-mar-pad
              %ul.tag-ul.no-mar-pad.mtop5
                %li.inline-display
                  %h4.tag-ul-h4.no-mar-pad.inline-display
                    = cat.name
                    \-
                - cat.subs.each do |sub|
                  %li.tag-ul-li.inline-display
                    = sub.name
                    for rent
                  |
